    <item>
      <title>Version 0.2.0</title>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 16:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>2</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description>&lt;style&gt;
body { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: -apple-system-label; }
h2 { font-size: 15px; margin: 16px 0 8px; }
h3 { font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0 6px; }
ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 4px 0; }
li { margin: 2px 0; }
code { background: -apple-system-quaternary-label; padding: 1px 4px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 12px; }
a { color: -apple-system-blue; text-decoration: none; }
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;New Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Menu bar status text&lt;/strong&gt;: Show connected time, server location, or both next to the menu bar icon. Optional colored icon (green/orange) for connection state.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global keyboard shortcut&lt;/strong&gt;: Configurable hotkey to toggle VPN from anywhere. Falls back to top favourite if no server is selected.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Connection notifications&lt;/strong&gt;: Native macOS notifications on connect, disconnect, unexpected drops, and failures. Actionable Disconnect/Reconnect buttons.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;App Intents&lt;/strong&gt;: Connect VPN, Disconnect VPN, Toggle VPN, and Get VPN Status available in Shortcuts, Siri, and Spotlight. Server picker with fuzzy search.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Fixes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sparkle gentle reminders for menu bar app&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Session expiry in Devices tab now shows "Log Out" instead of broken "Retry"&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Changelog&lt;/strong&gt;: https://github.com/SuperManifolds/Burrow/compare/v0.1.0...v0.2.0&lt;/p&gt;</description>
